description: Returns a paginated list of your schedule groups.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: Indicates whether there are additional results to retrieve. If the value is null, there are no more results.

nested_items.name: ScheduleGroups
nested_items.description: The schedule groups that match the specified criteria.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the schedule group.

nested_items.name: CreationDate
nested_items.description: The time at which the schedule group was created.

nested_items.name: LastModificationDate
nested_items.description: The time at which the schedule group was last modified.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the schedule group.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: Specifies the state of the schedule group.
